data.description: Newly built in 2021, this 3BR + loft home has already had additional upgrades made, and is ready for you to move on in! Wonderful floorplan features spacious Great Room w/ gorgeous custom accent wall + upgraded carpet; open kitchen w/ 42" cabinets, new backsplash, center island (w/ storage!) and upgraded lighting fixtures; and separate dining room. Upstairs you'll find the perfect loft space, convenient upper level laundry, and three good sized bedrooms. And don't miss that extra-deep storage closet at the end of the hall! HUGE Primary Suite with attached bath and DUAL walk-in closets! Lovey lot with large yard and a pond view! 2 car garage with additional 3'x8' bump-out (extra storage or room for that pick-up truck!). This one has it all!
